[[飓风多利安_(2019年)|飓风多利安]]是有纪录以来袭击[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]的最强飓风，于2019年9月上旬对[[阿巴科群岛|阿巴科群岛]]和[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]构成重大破坏，风暴强度以及在巴哈马附近缓慢的移动速度均打破多项纪录。多利安是[[2019年大西洋飓风季|2019年大西洋飓风季]]形成的第五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，第四场获命名的风暴，第二场飓风和首场大型飓风<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | type = Database | publisher = United States National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200612204920/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2019-052520.txt | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | date = 2020-05-25 | archivedate = 2020-06-12 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2019-052520.txt}}</ref>{{#tag:ref|大型飓风指强度按[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级]]达到三级或以上的飓风<ref>{{cite web | title = Saffir-Simpson Hurricane Wind Scale | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutsshws.php | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archive-date = 2020-07-20 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720052116/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/aboutsshws.php}}</ref>。|group="注"}}。气旋源自8月19日离开非洲西海岸向西移动的[[东风波|东风波]]，于8月24日组织成热带低气压，而且当天就增强成热带风暴。

受干燥空气和[[风切变|垂直风切变]]的共同影响，多利安成型后几天强化幅度很小。8月27日，风暴先后[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]和[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]后进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。圣卢西亚的山地严重扰乱气旋结构，促使系统中心在原本位置北面重新形成。风暴的移动路线比气象机构预计更偏北面和东面，于8月28日经过[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]东部。与此同时，减弱的风切变和温暖的[[海面温度|海面温度]]促使多利安进入[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]上空后升级成一级飓风。8月29日，多利安一度停止强化，但次日又开始[[快速增强|快速增强]]。在此期间，飓风受北面亚热带水域形成[[高压脊|高压脊]]的影响转向西北偏西，然后又转朝西侧移动。9月1日，风暴强度按[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风风力等级]]进入最高的五级飓风标准，并在当天达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]295公里、中心气压910[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，26.87[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度并登陆巴哈马[[埃尔博岛|埃尔博岛]]。{{#tag:ref|根据美国国家飓风中心的既定标准，[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]和位置如属估计数值，则用最接近的五的倍数表示；如果是直接测量值，则四舍五入取整。如无特殊说明，所有风速数值均为一分钟持续风速。气压值也是按四舍五入取毫巴和百帕值，英寸汞柱保留两位小数。|group="注"}}

9月2日，风暴稳步减弱，而且经过[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]上空期间移动速度逐渐放缓。9月3日，气旋强度跌破大型飓风标准并开始加速北上。9月5日，多利安在行经温暖的[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]期间强度短暂回升到三级飓风标准，但在转向东北逼近[[外滩群岛|外滩群岛]]期间又因风切变增多再度减弱。9月6日，气旋登陆[[哈特拉斯角|哈特拉斯角]]时强度已降至二级飓风下限。来自[[西风带|西风带]]的影响越来越强，多利安于9月7日开始失去热带天气系统特征并经过[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]上空，次日在[[圣罗伦斯湾|圣罗伦斯湾]]上空完全转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，最终于9月9日被更大规模的温带气旋吸收。

== 形成并经过小安的列斯群岛 ==
飓风多利安源自2019年8月19日离开非洲西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]（即拉长的[[低压槽|低压槽]]）<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | last1 = Avila | first1 = Lixion | last2 = Stewart | first2 = Stacy | last3 = Berg | first3 = Robbie | last4 = Hagen | first4 = Andrew | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Dorian | archivedate = 2020-04-30 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL052019_Dorian.pdf | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200430042603/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL052019_Dorian.pdf | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2020-04-20}}</ref>。在此期间，东风波的大部分[[对流|对流]]（[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动）距中心尚有一段距离，位于[[几内亚|几内亚]]和[[塞内加尔|塞内加尔]]附近内陆，东风波北部雷暴受到附近大量撒哈拉沙尘的限制<ref>{{cite web | last1 = Torres | first1 = Maria | title = Eastern Pacific Tropical Weather Discussion [205 PM EDT, Mon Aug 19, 2019] | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2019/TWDAT.201908191805.txt | publisher = National Hurricane Center | series = Tropical Weather Discussion | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190902182712/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2019/TWDAT.201908191805.txt | archive-date = 2019-09-02 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。东风波向西经过大西洋低纬度海域，大部分对流在此期间消散，但在8月22日又发展出低气压区。虽然所在水域存在中等强度[[风切变|垂直风切变]]，但系统仍在组织。<ref name="TCR" />8月23日，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]初步预测继续西进的系统会以缓慢速度发展<ref>{{cite report | last1 = Beven | first1 = Jack | title = Tropical Weather Outlook [800 AM EDT, Fri Aug 23, 2019] | archivedate = 2020-07-08 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200708120742/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?basin=atl&fdays=5&current_issuance=201908231435 | series = NHC Graphical Outlook Archive | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/xgtwo/gtwo_archive.php?current_issuance=201908231435&basin=atl&fdays=5 | date = 2019-08-23 | publisher = National Hurricane Center}}</ref>，但系统实际上却于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月24日早上六点在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]东南偏东方向约1295公里洋面组织成热带低气压<ref name="TCR" />。

[[File:Dorian_2019-08-26_1705Z.jpg|thumb]]]]

刚形成的热带低气压东南方向[[外流_(气象学)|外流]]受到中等强度东向风切变限制<ref>{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | title = Tropical Depression Five Discussion Number 1 | archivedate = 2020-01-25 | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.001.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200125044415/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.001.shtml }}</ref>。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天下午18点，气旋中层已发展出15公里宽的[[风眼|眼状特征]]，周围有[[雨带|带状]]特征重重包裹，气象机构将其升级成热带风暴并以“多利安”（{{lang|en|Dorian}}）命名<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | title = Tropical Storm Dorian Discussion Number 2 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.002.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190907042537/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.002.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。风暴起初因所在水域[[海面温度|海面温度]]高逐渐增强，但此后几天因中层大气干燥和风切变的共同影响基本停止强化<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Disc 4">{{cite report | last = Blake | first = Eric | title = Tropical Storm Dorian Discussion Number 4 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.004.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-25 | archivedate = 2019-08-25 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190825232313/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.004.shtml}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}8月27日凌晨1点30分，多利安以[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时85公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]巴巴多斯，进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]<ref name="TCR" />。此时的[[气象雷达|复合雷达]]图像表明系统缺乏强劲的内部核心<ref>{{cite report | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Tropical Storm Dorian Discussion Number  12 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.012.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190901145207/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.012.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-01 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}上午11点左右，风暴又以同等强度登陆[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]，岛上山区扰乱系统的下层环流<ref name="TCR" />。不久，多利安的中心在偏北方向重新发展，同时对流在干燥空气、[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]和[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]共同影响下波动。雷达显示气旋多次发展出宽约15公里的风眼，但很快就被中层大气中的干燥空气侵蚀。<ref name="Disc 14">{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | title = Tropical Storm Dorian Discussion Number  14 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.014.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190828155414/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.014.shtml | archivedate = 2019-08-28 | deadurl = no}}</ref>

[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]北面的[[冷心低压|中到上层低气压区]]导致[[高压脊|高压脊]]出现薄弱环节，风暴很快就略朝西北转向<ref name="Disc 16" />。气象部门起初预测多利安会登陆伊斯帕尼奥拉岛并在岛上减弱甚至消散，但系统实际上因中心在北面重组偏移预定路线，8月28日已抵达[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]东部<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Disc 14" />。风暴结构这天开始改善，带状特征更加明显且有部分风眼墙形成<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Disc 16">{{cite report | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Tropical Storm Dorian Discussion Number  16 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.016.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191226232005/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.016.shtml | archivedate = 2019-12-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。增强成一级飓风后，气旋于{{lang|en|UTC}}当天下午15点30分和18点分别登陆[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]的[[圣克罗伊岛|圣克罗伊岛]]和[[圣托马斯岛_(美属维尔京群岛)|圣托马斯岛]]。多利安的云层格局继续组织，[[卫星影像|卫星影像]]上的风眼更加明显。受[[佛罗里达海峡|佛罗里达海峡]]上空的上层低气压区和大西洋副热带高压脊之间气流影响，飓风朝西北方向移动。<ref name="TCR" />气象机构预计，风暴会因中层大气湿度增加、海面水温接近或超过29[[摄氏度|摄氏度]]，风切变少等利好因素共同影响继续增强。飓风强度已经提升，风眼更加清晰，<ref>{{cite report | last = Pasch | first = Richard | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  19 | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190831171835/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.019.shtml | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.019.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2019-08-31}}</ref>，但在干燥空气和西南向风切变影响下一度停上强化<ref>{{cite report | last = Berg | first = Robbie | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  20 | archivedate = 2019-12-27 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.020.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191227145548/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.020.shtml}}</ref>。8月29日晚，[[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|美国国家海洋和大气管理局]]的[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机发现同心风眼墙，表明飓风内已开始[[眼牆置換循環|眼牆置換循環]]。飞机还发现气旋中心气压下降，但在继续朝西北移动期间风速没有提升<ref>{{cite report | last = Brown | first = Daniel | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  21 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.021.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190831171835/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.021.shtml | archivedate = 2019-08-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 快速增强并登陆巴哈马 ==
[[File:Dorian_2019-09-01_2000Z.jpg|thumb]]

8月30日早上，多利亚已完成眼墙置换循环并恢复增强趋势。上层低气压区促使飓风回转南下，然后又在西侧形成的大西洋副热带高压脊影响下转向西北偏西，进入风切变少、相对湿度高、海面温度达29摄氏度的高度利好环境。<ref name="TCR" />风暴向西移动直逼巴哈马西北部<ref>{{cite report | last = Brown | first = Daniel | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  27 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.027.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190831171828/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.027.shtml | archivedate = 2019-08-31 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月30日18点在巴哈马西北部以东约715公里海域达到大型飓风标准<ref name="TCR" />。当天深夜，气旋的风眼内已经没有云层遮挡，周围由深层对流环绕，同时西北方向风眼墙还持续爆发闪电，预示飓风会进一步强化<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  26 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.026.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-30 | archivedate = 2019-08-31 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190831171816/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.026.shtml}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last = Cappucci | first = Matthew | title = Lightning barrage in Hurricane Dorian may signal rapid intensification | archive-date = 2019-12-20 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/08/30/lightning-barrage-hurricane-dorian-may-signal-rapid-intensification/ | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | newspaper = The Washington Post | date = 2019-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191220052242/https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/08/30/lightning-barrage-hurricane-dorian-may-signal-rapid-intensification/}}</ref>。经飓风猎人侦察机确认，风暴在{{lang|en|UTC}}8月31日凌晨0点[[快速增强|快速增强]]成四级飓风，地面风速接近每小时215公里<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | last1 = Cangialosi | first1 = John | last2 = Latto | first2 = Andrew | title = Hurricane Dorian Tropical Cyclone Update | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.update.08310027.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-08-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191223141600/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.update.08310027.shtml | archivedate = 2019-12-23 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。气旋的卫星影像更显清晰，风眼更加鲜明且直径稳定在22公里左右。风眼还开始呈现明显的[[風眼#体育场效应|体育场效应]]，风眼墙的云层从表面向外凸出，这种情况往往在非常强烈的热带气旋上才会出现。<ref name="TCR" />

{{lang|en|UTC}}9月1日早上6点，多利安成为五级飓风，风力时速达270公里<ref name="TCR" />。{{lang|en|UTC}}中午12点左右，美国国家飓风中心估计气旋的一分钟持续风速已达每小时285公里，成为有纪录以来吹袭巴哈马的最强飓风。{{lang|en|UTC}}当天下午15点前不久，飓风猎人测得飞行高度层的风眼墙内风力时速达295公里，[[微波辐射计|步进频率微波辐射计]]所测风速更达每小时315公里，侦察机投放的[[投落送|投落送]]测得时速326公里地面阵风。<ref name="Strongest NW Bahamas">{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  33 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.033.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | date = 2019-09-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190907042555/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.033.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-07 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>多利安此后几小时继续强化，最终达到的最高强度为最大持续风速每小时295公里，最低中心气压910毫巴（百帕，26.87英寸汞柱）。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月1日下午16点40分，飓风以最高强度登陆[[阿巴科群岛|阿巴科群岛]]埃尔博岛（{{lang|en|Elbow Cay}}），成为有可靠纪录以来登陆巴哈马的最强飓风。<ref name="TCR" />

[[File:Dorian_2019-09-02_1520Z_by_ISS-60.jpg|thumb]]观察位于大巴哈马岛上空的飓风多利安]]

穿过阿巴科群岛期间，风暴北侧的高压脊减弱，转向气流减少，导致多利安的移动速度放缓。气旋缓慢向西移动，强度略有回落，于{{lang|en|UTC}}9月2日凌晨2点15分以风力时速285公里强度从[[大巴哈马岛|大巴哈马岛]]南骑角（{{lang|en|South Riding Point}}）附近登陆。六小时后，系统从大巴哈马岛北岸回到海上，虽因陆地和深海冷水[[上升流|上升]]导致风眼增大，风速减慢，但仍有五级飓风标准。<ref name="TCR" />多利安此后几小时逐渐减弱，强度在{{lang|en|UTC}}9月3日早上六点回落至三级飓风范围。风暴在大巴哈马岛北岸近海的移动速度极其缓慢，从{{lang|en|UTC}}9月2日正午12点至9月3日正午12点整整24小时仅行进约49公里，整个大马哈马岛因此持续三天的风速最低都达热带风暴强度。<ref name="TCR" />风眼墙在该岛部分地区停留超过25小时，其中包括多利安尚处五级飓风强度时期，同时霍尔角（{{lang|en|Halls Point}}）在风眼内持续超过11小时<ref>{{cite news | last = Cappucci | first = Matthew | title = Dorian’s horrific eyewall slammed Grand Bahama Island for 40 hours straight | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191214034048/https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/09/03/dorians-horrific-eyewall-slammed-grand-bahama-island-hours-straight/ | archivedate = 2019-12-14 | date = 2019-09-03 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/09/03/dorians-horrific-eyewall-slammed-grand-bahama-island-hours-straight/?noredirect=on | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | newspaper = The Washington Post}}</ref>。飓风这段时间在巴哈马产生的降雨总量估计高达900毫米<ref>{{cite web | last = Jenner | first = Lynn | title = Sep. 04, 2019 – NASA Estimates Hurricane Dorian’s Massive Bahama Rainfall Totals | url = https://blogs.nasa.gov/hurricanes/2019/09/04/dorian-atlantic-ocean-17/ | website = NASA Blogs | publisher = National Aeronautics and Space Administration | date = 2019-09-04 | accessdate = 2020-07-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190905145324/https://blogs.nasa.gov/hurricanes/2019/09/04/dorian-atlantic-ocean-17/ | archive-date = 2019-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，风暴潮超过6.1米<ref name="TCR" />。
{{clear}}

== 转向北上，转变成温带气旋和消散 ==
[[File:Dorian_2019-09-07_1730Z.jpg|thumb]]]]

9月3日晚，[[美国东部|美国东部]]上空向东移动的中层低压槽促使气旋北上，开始朝西北方向的[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]移动<ref name="TCR" />。与此同时，风眼扩大并出现云层遮挡，边缘变得模糊，侦察机和浮标收集的数据表明多利安风场逐渐扩大<ref>{{cite report | last = Brown | first = Daniel | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  41 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.041.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190905071234/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.041.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。次日，飓风因行经洋面水温降低、风切变增强而缓慢减弱<ref name="TCR" />。风暴移动速度逐渐提升，风眼的清晰度反复波动<ref>{{cite report | last = Brown | first = Daniel | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  42 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.042.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190903210632/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.042.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref name="4 September 2019">{{cite report | last = Pasch | first = Richard | title  =Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  44 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.044.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190904105021/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.044.shtml | date = 2019-09-04 | archivedate = 2019-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。不久，多利安又因温暖的[[墨西哥湾暖流|墨西哥湾暖流]]再度增强<ref name="TCR" />，风眼墙的云层开始降温<ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  46 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.046.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190904211545/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.046.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风眼内的云层消散，周围由深层对流环绕后，气旋于{{lang|en|UTC}}9月5日凌晨0点在[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]]近海达到最大持续风速每小时185公里的第二波强度高峰，又一次成为三级飓风<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  47 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.047.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190905131127/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.047.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。约12小时后，风暴在沿[[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]]海岸移动期间开始逐渐减弱<ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  49 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.049.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190905155142/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.049.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-05 | deadurl = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  52 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.052.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190906140211/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.052.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。飓风加速向东北移动，于{{lang|en|UTC}}9月6日中午12点30分左右以风力时速155公里，最低气压957毫巴（百帕，28.26英寸汞柱）强度登陆[[北卡罗来纳州|北卡罗来纳州]]哈特拉斯角（{{lang|en|Cape Hatteras}}），该州风力大多在一级飓风范围，最高风速基本位于海上<ref name="TCR" />。虽然强度已大幅降低，但风暴的风眼依旧层次分明，周围是深层对流层层环绕<ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  53 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.053.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190906192537/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.053.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-06 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

9月7日清晨，多利安开始朝[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]转变。卫星图像显示风暴结构不再对称，风眼完全消失。<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  55 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.055.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191224213140/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.055.shtml | archivedate = 2019-12-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>飓风结构在强烈的西南向风切变摧残下瓦解，大部分对流移位至中心东侧和北面<ref>{{cite report | last = Cangialosi | first = John | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  56 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.056.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-07 | archivedate = 2020-07-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721163150/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.056.shtml}}</ref>。不久，多利安与东北方向发展的暖锋相连，冷空气云层开始侵入气旋西南面<ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Hurricane Dorian Discussion Number  57 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721163406/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.057.shtml | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.057.shtml? | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | deadurl = no | date = 2019-09-07 | archivedate = 2020-07-22}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月7日下午18点左右，风暴已经失去大部分热带天气系统特征，不再属于热带气旋<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Disc 59" />，但美国国家飓风中心认为风暴仍然威胁[[加拿大大西洋省份|加拿大大西洋省份]]，所以继续发布公告<ref name="Disc 59">{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Dorian Discussion Number  59 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.059.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190913112748/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.059.shtml | archivedate = 2019-09-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。在此期间，上空经过的卫星[[散射仪|散射仪]]所获数据表明，风暴内部风速在每小时145至160公里范围<ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Hurricane Dorian Special Discussion Number  58 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.058.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191220094654/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.058.shtml | archivedate = 2019-12-20 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}当晚22点左右，多利安从[[新斯科舍省|新斯科舍省]]桑布罗克里克（{{lang|en|Sambro Creek}}）附近登陆<ref name="TCR" />。气旋开始嵌入温带西向气流，并逐渐向东转向<ref>{{cite report | last = Avila | first = Lixion | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Dorian Discussion Number  60 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.060.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-07 | archivedate = 2020-07-21 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721165907/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.060.shtml}}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月8日早上6点，位于[[圣罗伦斯湾|圣罗伦斯湾]]上空的风暴已经完全转变成温带气旋<ref name="TCR" />，云层格局逐渐消失，到下午18点风速已降至热带风暴范围<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Dorian Discussion Number  62 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721170159/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.062.shtml | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.062.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-08 | archivedate = 2020-07-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite report | last = Beven | first = Jack | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Dorian Discussion Number  63 | date = 2019-09-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200721170346/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.063.shtml | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.063.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | archivedate = 2020-07-21}}</ref>。9月9日，气旋中心附近几乎没有显著对流。不久，多利安进入北大西洋，附近的[[拉布拉多海|拉布拉多海]]海面温度不足十摄氏度。{{lang|en|UTC}}9月9日早上六点，多利安在[[纽芬兰与拉布拉多省|纽芬兰]]东北部被更大规模的温带气旋吸收。<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Dorian Discussion Number  64 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.064.shtml? | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | date = 2019-09-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191225091238/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2019/al05/al052019.discus.064.shtml | archivedate = 2019-12-25}}</ref>

== 纪录 ==
{{登陆时最强烈的大西洋飓风|align=right}}
多利安达到最高强度后打破多项纪录。多利安的最大持续风速达每小时295公里，与[[1935年劳动节飓风|1935年劳动节飓风]]、[[颶風吉爾伯特|颶風吉爾伯特]]和[[飓风威尔玛|威尔玛]]一起在有纪录以来所有的大西洋飓风中并列第二<ref>{{cite report | publisher = American Meteorological Society, Journal of Climate | date = 2014-08-15 | last8 = Dickinson | first8 = Michael | page = 6114 | url = https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/landsea-et-al-jclimate-2014.pdf | title = A Reanalysis of the 1931–43 Atlantic Hurricane Database | last7 = Strahan-Sakoskie | first7 = Donna | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200222201705/https://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/landsea-et-al-jclimate-2014.pdf | archive-date = 2020-02-22 | last1 = Landsea | first1 = Chris | last2 = Hagen | first2 = Andrew | last3 = Bredemeyer | first3 = William | last4 = Carrasco | first4 = Cristina | last5 = Glenn | first5 = David | last6 = Santiago | first6 = Adrian | deadurl = no | format = PDF | access-date = 2020-07-22 }}</ref><ref name="Records">{{cite report | title = Hurricane Dorian Meteorological Records/Notable Facts Recap | publisher = Colorado State University | date = 2019-09-03 | deadurl = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191214051050/https://tropical.colostate.edu/media/sites/111/2019/09/Hurricane_Dorian_Records.pdf | url = https://tropical.colostate.edu/media/sites/111/2019/09/Hurricane_Dorian_Records.pdf | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | archive-date = 2019-12-14}}</ref>，仅次于风力时速305公里的[[颶風艾倫_(1980年)|飓风艾伦]]<ref>{{cite report | title = Preliminary Report: Hurricane Allen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | url = https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1980-prelim/allen/prelim08.gif | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190904170157/https://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1980-prelim/allen/prelim08.gif | archivedate = 2019-09-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。同时，多利安还是历史上在[[热带|热带]]以外洋面达到强度最高的飓风<ref name="Records" />。风暴以最高风速登陆，是有纪录以来袭击阿巴科群岛的最强气旋<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Records" />，也是除[[1932年巴哈马飓风|1932年巴哈马飓风]]外唯一登陆阿巴科群岛的五级飓风<ref name="MSNAbaco">{{cite news | author1 = Digital Writers | title = Catastrophic Hurricane Dorian could come dangerously close to Florida | url = https://www.msn.com/en-ca/news/world/catastrophic-hurricane-dorian-could-come-dangerously-close-to-florida/ar-AAGGwi8 | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | publisher = [[MSN|MSN]] | date = 2019-09-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190907042530/https://www.msn.com/en-ca/news/world/catastrophic-hurricane-dorian-could-come-dangerously-close-to-florida/ar-AAGGwi8 | archive-date = 2019-09-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。此外，多利安还与1935年劳动节飓风并列成为登陆时持续风速最高的大西洋飓风<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Freedman | first1 = Andrew | last2 = Samenow | first2 = Jason | title = Historic Hurricane Dorian unleashing 'catastrophic' blow in northern Bahamas, hurricane warnings posted for Florida's east coast | date = 2019-09-01 | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/09/01/catastrophic-hurricane-dorian-unleashes-devastating-blow-northern-bahamas-takes-aim-southeast-us/?noredirect=on | newspaper = The Washington Post | accessdate = 2020-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200607105442/https://www.washingtonpost.com/weather/2019/09/01/catastrophic-hurricane-dorian-unleashes-devastating-blow-northern-bahamas-takes-aim-southeast-us/ | archive-date = 2020-06-07 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。多利安达到五级强度后，[[2019年大西洋飓风季|2019年大西洋飓风季]]已是连续第四个形成至少一场五级飓风的大西洋飓风季<ref name="C5" />{{#tag:ref|[[2016年大西洋飓风季|2016]]至2019年间，每年大西洋飓风季都形成至少一个五级飓风，同样创下新纪录<ref name="C5">{{Cite web | url = https://weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/2019-09-01-hurricane-dorian-atlantic-hurricane-category-five-history | title = Hurricane Dorian Becomes the 5th Atlantic Category 5 in 4 Years | website = The Weather Channel | access-date = 2020-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200622221901/https://weather.com/storms/hurricane/news/2019-09-01-hurricane-dorian-atlantic-hurricane-category-five-history | archive-date = 2020-06-22 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。

多利安在巴哈马附近缓慢的移动速度同样创下多项纪录。前后24小时间，多利安只行进49公里，是[[1965年大西洋飓风季|1965年]][[飓风贝特西|飓风贝特西]]过后移动最慢的大型飓风<ref name="Records" />。气旋的部分风眼墙持续冲击大阿巴科岛和大巴哈马岛约22小时，刷新大西洋盆地五级飓风吹袭陆地的时长纪录<ref name="strongest, slowest hurricane">{{cite web | archive-date = 2020-07-20 | deadurl = no | first = Doyle | last = Rice | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200720204634/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2019/09/06/hurricane-dorian-becomes-strongest-slowest-hurricane-hit-bahamas-record/2232225001/ | url = https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2019/09/06/hurricane-dorian-becomes-strongest-slowest-hurricane-hit-bahamas-record/2232225001/ | title = Dorian's legacy: The slowest, strongest hurricane to ever hit the Bahamas | newspaper = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2019-09-07 | accessdate = 2020-07-22 }}</ref>。
